HOW CAN WE HELP YOU?

Frequently Asked Questions

Are lessons recorded or live?

Lessons are both live and recorded. We have the largest number of live lessons of any IELTS course in the world to suit all time zones, but we also know many of our students want the convenience of recorded lessons. Recordings of all live lessons are made available after the live lesson.

What if I need help?

There are several ways you can get help on the course. Firstly, we have many live Zoom sessions each day where you can speak live to a teacher. Secondly, you can also email us with your special VIP email and we will answer your questions 24/7. Finally, if you need a 1-1 session, we can speak with you on Zoom. You may also interact with the teachers during each lesson and inside the VIP community.

Is feedback live?

Yes. If you want to get feedback on your speaking, you can book a 1-1 Zoom session at a time that suits your schedule. All writing feedback is via 1-1 video feedback.

What is the course timing?

There are no timings. You are a VIP so you decide when you want us to teach you, help you, or give you feedback.

Is the payment secure?

100%. We use the best payment processor in the world and have never had a problem in more than 7 years of doing business.

How will I know I’m ready for my test?

We will tell you when you are ready based on your performance.

What happens if I fail?

Less than 2% of our students fail the test. If you do, you have lifetime help, support and guidance so we will help you pass next time at no extra cost.

Do you guarantee results?

No IELTS course can get 100% of their students the score they need. Any school that says they have a 100% success rate is lying. However, the only students who do not pass the test with us are students who don’t complete the course or don’t listen to our advice. If you do the work and listen to us, you have a 98% chance of getting the score you need.

Will Chris be my teacher?

Chris designs all the materials and presents all of the course modules. He also trains all of the teachers to give you the exact same advice as he would. However, Chris is human and cannot work 24/7 so our team of experts help him with teaching live lessons and giving feedback. Don’t worry; they are some of the best teachers in the world.

How can I contact you with another question?

Send an email to [email protected] and we will get back to you right away.
